Jeffrey Combs https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeffrey_Combs 0 Jeffrey Alan Combs (born September 9, 1954) is an American actor known for starring in horror films, such as Re-Animator, and appearances playing a number of characters in the Star Trek and the DC Animated Universe television franchises.
